flowy, comprehensible&lt;br&gt;
jargon is fun&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;in org-roam&lt;br&gt;
links when depth&lt;br&gt;
more speed&lt;br&gt;
good&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
